<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Hostel Management System</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #272c4a;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #f7403b;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #f7403b;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 18px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #4e528f;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Hostel Hub</h1>
    <p>Manage your hostels and student accommodations with ease. Simplify room allocation, check-ins, maintenance requests, and billing.</p>
    <a href="/stdlogin" class="button">Student</a>
    <a href="/adminlogin" class="button">Admin</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
